summary.English: Dr. Jeremy London, a board-certified cardiovascular surgeon, warns about heart disease risks and shares six habits he avoids to maintain his heart health.

summary.English: He advises against using alcohol-based mouthwash as it can impact blood pressure by disrupting beneficial bacteria in the mouth that produce nitric oxide.
